  "Description": "\u00c2\u00a9 Copyright 2020 Blue Cross and Blue Shield of Kansas City\n\nDESCRIPTION: Extract MBR_MCAID_INFO table data from IDS and load to file.\n\nCALLED BY : EdwMbrNoDriverSeq\n\nModifications:\n\n                           Project/                                                                                                                                                                                             Code                   Date\nDeveloper           Date              Altiris #                                  Change Description                                                                                      DataStage Project          Reviewer            Reviewed\n-------------------------  -------------------   -------------                              -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------      ---------------------------------   -------------------------     -------------------\nNeelima\nTummala            11/05/2020    US#300494                          Initial Development                                                                                       EnterpriseDev2              Jeyaprasanna      2020-11-18\n\nNeelima\nTummala            12/07/2020    US#300494                          Updated Incremental logic                                                                            EnterpriseDev2             Jeyaprasanna      2020-12-08\n\nAnnotations:\nJOB NAME: IdsEdwMbrMcaidInfoDExtr\nRead all the Data from IDS MBR_MCAID_INFO Table; Pull records based on LAST_UPDT_RUN_CYC_EXCTN_SK\nWrite Data into a Sequential file for Load Job IdsEdwMbrMcaidInfoDLoad.\n.\nAdd Defaults and Null Handling."
